{"tid":12835,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖！！陰莖被毒蛇咬到後的慘狀","createTime":"2016-11-29T22:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T00:18:00.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8217ab0096470c4825a66742d12ee4d08b7fadbc","tid":12835,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T22:17:54.000Z","msg":"圖：<a href=\"http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMicm1410237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FNEJMicm1410237&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O38C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=7eadacc0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMicm1410237</a><br />\n印度一名46歲男子日前在農地工作時，暫時想要小解，於是脫下褲子。就在這一瞬間，他的陰莖慘被黎凡特毒蛇(Levantine viper)狠咬，導致他的陰莖快速腫脹，該名男子趕緊就醫。近日《新英格蘭醫學期刊》(New England Journal of Medicine)就刊登該案例的相關照片，並看到陰莖被毒蛇咬後的慘狀。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，該名男子的陰莖被毒蛇咬後，馬上腫脹，而且毒液進入人體後，會破壞人體的正常凝血功能，可能因此出血不止，最後導致死亡。該名男子在注入抗毒蛇血清36小時之後，身體狀況逐漸恢復穩定。治療數日後，男子的陰莖逐漸消腫，傷口開始結痂，壞死的部分也逐漸有了再生跡象，2周後男子就恢復健康狀態。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;"},{"pid":"5b49ebb820d66ff26c6366d39c07c8b2782c355b","tid":12835,"uid":5751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:11:47.000Z","msg":"我屌 依啲就有圖"},{"pid":"a8d35e6650902c35b5acb117aeda75c93d27cc8c","tid":12835,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:14:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屌 依啲就有圖</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14db327cd48c7fb2113574f011ad59dcda3cd0d","tid":12835,"uid":40607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:31:48.000Z","msg":"佢應該以痾尿都會有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67492c7af5dbbd32d88c4cf56e97fe88228cf099","tid":12835,"uid":42372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/